/* Table: "BC_ChangeTypeDictionary" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_ChangeTypeDictionary"
(
"TypeID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ChangeTypeCode" INTEGER,
"BCTypeName" NVARCHAR2(200),
"IsEffect" INTEGER,
constraint PK_BC_CHANGETYPEDICTIONARY primary key ("TypeID")
);

60:子品牌系列变更';
